headline: Is It Too Late to Consider Keysight After Its 31% 2025 Rally?
summary: Wondering if Keysight Technologies is still a smart buy at these levels, or if the best gains are already behind it? You are not alone, and the answer is more nuanced than a simple yes or no. The stock has quietly put together an impressive run, up 6.3% over the last week, 16.4% over the past month, and 30.9% year to date, with a 5 year gain of 66.7% that has many investors rethinking its upside.
